  <description type="morphology">Stems with rhizoids in 1 (or 2) transverse rows on stem just below leaf insertion and on stem leaf proximal abaxial costa surface. Leaves straight, not or little twisted distally, tapering from base to apex, widest at base; apex long-acuminate. Seta reddish, darker proximally, lighter distally, 3–4.5(–5) cm, slightly twisted when dry, straight to somewhat flexuose. Calyptra naked.</description>
